menu2.name: Peppermint Bark Ice Cream Bar
menu2.details: Our peppermint bark ice cream bars start with decadent white chocolate ice cream, dipped in thick, dark chocolate, then speckled with cool peppermint candy pieces.

menu2.name: Ruby Cacao Ice Cream Bar
menu2.details: Indulge in the decadent crunch of a ruby cacao shell and our creamy sweet cream ice cream, for a sensorial experience of luscious smoothness with berry fruity notes.

menu2.name: Caramel Cone Ice Cream Bar
menu2.details: Your favorite Caramel Pizzelle Bar, renamed. Golden ribbons of caramel in creamy vanilla gelato, enrobed in rich milk chocolate and crunchy italian style cone pieces.

menu2.name: Chocolate Dark Chocolate Ice Cream Bar
menu2.details: Between the classic rich and creamy chocolate ice cream inside, and the thick and crunchy dark chocolate coating finely drizzled on the outside, this is a chocolate connoisseur's delight.

menu2.name: Irish Cream Cookie Squares
menu2.details: A rich chocolate cookie topped with ice cream that’s infused with Irish Cream before the entire square is dipped in decadent dark chocolate. *Contains Less Than 0.5% Alcohol by Volume.

menu2.name: Vanilla Milk Chocolate Almond Ice Cream Bar
menu2.details: We start with pure, sweet vanilla and blend it with sweet, fresh cream to make our incredibly smooth vanilla ice cream. Then we dip it in a crunchy roasted almond and milk chocolate coating.
